Summary: Very large boomerang shaped UFO came out of the moutians hovered vertically at maybe 2000 feet at the speed of light went east ward
divs: sighting detailsmy wife and i were sitting on our back porch at about 10:00 at night. our house faced southwest from highlands ranch \ daniels gate park. we watched an obeject that was a very large craft. maybe even a mile to two miles wide. the craft was boomeranged in shape. the craft came from out of the mountains and it hovered vertically at about 2,000 to four thousand feet about the mountian. the craft stayed stationary for about two to three minutes. we both looked at each other stunned. the craft went from a stationary position to what seemed like the speed of light east ward where it disappeared. the craft at no time made any sound. it was completetly solid white in color. the boomerang had hard corners not soft like a boomerang. it was a geomoetrical hard angle boomerang that rose vertically and stayed vertical.
